dialogue.dialogueText: *Woah* Who is this really old man...
But who are you... and why does my head hurt so bad...?
I am Tiny Town's Village Head! The Dark Wizard has taken everyone in the town hostage to zap them of their power. You must defeat him, only you can save Tiny Town.
It seems your injuries are much worse than before.
It's not the first time I had to drag you out of battle.
Do you not know who you are?
Crap... guess we are starting over. We have a lot of catching up to do.
Let's start with choosing your class.
Would you like to be a Warrior, Wizard or Archer?
I want to be a Warrior.
I want to be a Magician.
I want to be an Archer.
Warriors are known to be the most durable of fighters. With high vitality, defense and MaxHP they can take on the most damage and last the longest in battle.
Wizards are a crafty bunch. With high intelligence and the ability to heal, they are able to use their wide range of skills to battle.

Archers are extremely fast and deal large amounts of physical and magic damage. With high attack speed and a good balance of magic and physical attacks, they are very proficient in battle. They don't last long however...
Are you sure you want to be a Warrior?
Are you sure you want to be a Wizard?
Are you sure you want to be an Archer?
How can I help you today?
You already have an active Quest!
It's too dangerous! You are Lvl [level]. You need to be Level 12 to fight the Dark Wizard!
